    <item>
      <title>iPhone 制造商鸿海借助人工智能实现营收反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/iphone-maker-hon-hai-sustains-revenue-rebound-with-help-from-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鸿海精密工业股份有限公司上季度营收增长加速，由于推动人工智能发展的服务器需求抵消了智能手机销售疲软的影响，该公司保持了反弹势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/iphone-maker-hon-hai-sustains-revenue-rebound-with-help-from-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 08:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
